"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:24:31.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=2udh5xhCYt10QHcWxQFnE7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d9522e45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>？那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『真心話室』（星期一至日，下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"d9508ce35ec81d3c54ea3a2bbcfe8a1d85b0e5b4","tid":804661,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 自殺po連囝仲唔做野"},{"pid":"768ff97aeda62493673fb6b1077b0bb664d96b47","tid":804661,"uid":124667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"嘈夠未呀 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893e68e9bb891a4f9d756d3fcc75ed8fa96916e1","tid":804661,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9508ce35ec81d3c54ea3a2bbcfe8a1d85b0e5b4","tid":804661,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 自殺po連囝仲唔做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"無牙"},{"pid":"ae639357a6b7c77585a34120d5811f3495916629","tid":804661,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"堅系跳制ツ"},{"pid":"56229eaf176892903ad67360a70f2e144e8b9a47","tid":804661,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"jm9"},{"pid":"03159dd2d249c3924c6e989d1acd7f17cc87d38a","tid":804661,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"痴撚線😂😂"},{"pid":"62f9c3a3e0c7594d4b58f1a72e846d9baecd3ff0","tid":804661,"uid":30476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"